These commands will set up displaying the number
of deaths the player's have experienced when
showing the Tab list.

First define the objective:

  /scoreboard objectives add Deaths deathCount

Set players' known deathCount (if needed):

  /scoreboard players set PlayerName Deaths 3

PlayerName's deathCount will auto increment when
they die.

Set `Deaths` for display using command:

  /scoreboard objectives setdisplay list Deaths

You can use various displays.

  list      - player list when holding Tab
  sidebar   - to right of all player's screen
  belowName - as `sidebar` but under name

__END__
